{"word":"G2357 - θρησκός - thrēskós - thrace'-kos - Religious","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">θρησκός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">thrēskós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">thrace'-kos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Religious</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"தேவபக்தி - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"fearing or worshipping God; religious"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Probably from the base of <a href=\"#/G2360 - θροέω - throéō - thro-eh'-o/2360\">G2360</a>; <i>ceremonious</i> in worship (as <i>demonstrative</i>), that is, <i>pious:</i> - religious.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1479/1479\">G1479</a>, <a href=\"#/G2356/2356\">G2356</a>, <a href=\"#/G2357/2357\">G2357</a>"}]}